<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="meanwhile-n">meanwhile <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'miːnwaɪl/    美 /'miːnwaɪl/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>其时；其间</strong></h4>
<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-the-meanwhile-meantime">in the meanwhile / meantime</h3>
<p>1.<strong>在此期间；与此同时：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Please find a taxi, and in the meanwhile I’ll pack some food. 
你去叫辆出租车，趁这工夫我打包点吃的。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>It will be a big help if you go to the store and get what we need for dinner. <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ the meanwhile I’ll set the table.  （2013 浙江改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. In  </p></div>